WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:03.044
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:03.044 --> 00:05.046
NOW I KNOW YOU'VE BEEN
WORKING WITH MARGAUX AND
DIGGING UP DIRT ON ME.

00:05.046 --> 00:07.178
YOU KNOW, AS CRAZY
AS LOUISE MAY BE,

00:07.178 --> 00:09.840
I'M NOT GONNA HELP YOU
DO TO HER WHAT YOU DID TO ME.

00:09.840 --> 00:11.011
I MESSED UP.
 THIS IS OVER!

00:11.011 --> 00:13.094
WHY?
 BECAUSE I'M PREGNANT.

00:13.094 --> 00:14.845
MY FATHER
WAS ATTACKED TWICE.

00:14.845 --> 00:17.017
THE SECOND ATTACKER WAS FOUND
AT THE POLICE STATION HANGED.

00:17.017 --> 00:18.769
I BELIEVE THAT SOMEONE
WHO HAD THE POWER TO GET CLOSE

00:18.769 --> 00:19.850
MURDERED HIM.

00:19.850 --> 00:21.562
NO ONE ELSE
HAD ACCESS TO THAT ROOM

00:21.562 --> 00:22.943
EXCEPT ALVAREZ
AND THE FEDS.

00:22.943 --> 00:25.196
THE GUY COMING AFTER ME
IS MALCOLM BLACK.

00:25.196 --> 00:27.818
HE FORCED ME TO LAUNDER MONEY
OR HE WOULD KILL AMANDA.

00:27.818 --> 00:29.110
AND NOW I HAVE TO FIND HIM.

00:29.110 --> 00:30.741
DAVID OWES MALCOLM
A LOT OF MONEY.

00:30.741 --> 00:32.203
IF IT'S MONEY
THIS MALCOLM WANTS,

00:32.203 --> 00:33.414
THERE IS ANOTHER SOLUTION.

00:33.414 --> 00:34.705
I TRUST THAT YOU'LL GET THAT
IN THE RIGHT HANDS

00:34.705 --> 00:36.207
AND KEEP MINE CLEAN.

00:40.040 --> 00:41.622
Victoria:
TELL ME WHAT YOU CAN.

00:41.622 --> 00:44.165
HOW ABOUT I START WITH WHERE
I'VE BEEN THE LAST 10 YEARS?

00:44.165 --> 00:45.506
YOU WEREN'T IN THAT SILO,
WERE YOU?

00:45.506 --> 00:50.010
THERE'S A MAN
MORE DANGEROUS THAN CONRAD.

00:51.472 --> 00:54.175
Victoria:
HE'LL KILL US ALL!

00:54.175 --> 00:55.976
AS LONG AS MALCOLM BLACK IS OUT
THERE, OUR LIVES ARE IN DANGER.

00:55.976 --> 00:58.679
DAVID, YOU HAD NO RIGHT TO
KEEP ME IN THE DARK FOR SO LONG!

00:58.679 --> 01:00.351
I SHOULD'VE TOLD YOU
THE TRUTH SOONER,

01:00.351 --> 01:02.183
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT MALCOLM.

01:02.183 --> 01:03.234
I'M DEALING WITH HIM.

01:03.234 --> 01:04.815
THAT MAN
HAS ATTACKED YOU RELENTLESSLY.

01:04.815 --> 01:06.527
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
HE'LL BACK OFF NOW?

01:06.527 --> 01:08.359
BECAUSE HE VALUES HIS FREEDOM
MORE THAN MONEY.

01:08.359 --> 01:09.780
THREATENING HIM
WITH EVIDENCE

01:09.780 --> 01:11.402
IS A TEMPORARY SOLUTION
AT BEST, DAVID.

01:11.402 --> 01:13.614
GO TO THE FBI
AND ASK FOR PROTECTION.

01:13.614 --> 01:15.616
THEY CAN'T HELP US.
LOOK, I KNOW HOW TO STOP HIM.

01:15.616 --> 01:16.997
YOU GAVE AWAY MILLIONS
OF HIS FORTUNE.

01:16.997 --> 01:20.201
MEN LIKE HIM DO NOT STOP UNTIL
REPARATIONS HAVE BEEN MADE.

01:21.912 --> 01:24.004
EMILY HAS ENOUGH.

01:24.004 --> 01:25.916
NO.

01:25.916 --> 01:27.798
NO.

01:27.798 --> 01:29.590
NO, I WAS A PRISONER
FOR 10 YEARS.

01:29.590 --> 01:31.712
I'LL DIE
BEFORE I HAVE TO GIVE IN TO HIM.

01:31.712 --> 01:33.844
DAVID...

01:33.844 --> 01:35.976
EMILY IS A WAY OUT.

01:35.976 --> 01:37.558
GO TO HER.
ASK FOR HER HELP.

01:37.558 --> 01:39.270
LISTEN,
I WILL PROTECT US.

01:39.270 --> 01:41.222
BUT I NEED YOU
TO TRUST ME

01:41.222 --> 01:43.724
AND TO PROMISE ME
THAT YOU WILL NOT INTERFERE.

01:45.776 --> 01:47.107
I'LL DO WHAT'S BEST.

01:49.780 --> 01:52.153
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

01:52.153 --> 01:54.405
I'LL BE BACK TONIGHT.

01:59.119 --> 02:01.041
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

02:03.664 --> 02:04.665
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

02:04.665 --> 02:06.167
THANKS FOR MEETING ME
THIS MORNING.

02:06.167 --> 02:07.838
WE HAVE TO
MAKE THIS QUICK.

02:07.838 --> 02:10.511
I HAVE
A VERY BUSY DAY.

02:10.511 --> 02:16.016
YOU PROBABLY WANT
TO THINK ABOUT SLOWING...DOWN.

02:16.016 --> 02:17.057
LISTEN TO ME.

02:17.057 --> 02:20.221
I MADE SOME CALLS,
AND I GOT YOU IN WITH DR. VIONI.

02:20.221 --> 02:21.682
SHE'S THE BEST OB-GYN
IN THE CITY.

02:21.682 --> 02:23.264
NO, I DIDN'T ASK YOU
TO DO THAT.

02:23.264 --> 02:24.855
I DIDN'T ASK YOU
TO DO ANYTHING.

02:24.855 --> 02:26.267
I'M NOT ASKING YOU
TO TAKE ME BACK,

02:26.267 --> 02:27.818
BUT WE HAVE TO
FIGURE THIS OUT.

02:27.818 --> 02:30.571
NO MATTER HOW YOU FEEL ABOUT ME,
OUR CHILD NEEDS A FATHER.

02:30.571 --> 02:32.903
A FATHER?
LIKE THE ONE YOU HAD?

02:34.905 --> 02:36.617
I'M SORRY.

02:36.617 --> 02:38.279
BUT THE BABY
HAS CHANGED THINGS FOR ME.

02:38.279 --> 02:39.870
AND WE BOTH
HAVE TO ADMIT

02:39.870 --> 02:41.912
SOMETHING HAS CHANGED IN YOU,
AS WELL.

02:41.912 --> 02:43.584
I CAN'T TRUST
THE MAN YOU'VE BECOME,

02:43.584 --> 02:45.586
NOT WHEN SOMEONE ELSE'S LIFE
DEPENDS ON IT.

02:45.586 --> 02:47.418
JUST...LOOK, I UNDERSTAND
YOU'RE STILL ANGRY.

02:47.418 --> 02:48.709
OH, I'M NOT ANGRY.

02:48.709 --> 02:50.211
I'M REALISTIC.

02:50.211 --> 02:52.052
YOU'RE VERY GOOD
AT SAYING THE PERFECT THING

02:52.052 --> 02:53.133
WHEN LIFE IS EASY,

02:53.133 --> 02:55.466
BUT WHEN CHOICES GET HARD,
YOU RUN AWAY.

02:55.466 --> 02:57.097
[ ELEVATOR DOOR OPENS ]

02:57.097 --> 02:59.099
THERE'S ONLY ONE OF US RUNNING,
MARGAUX.

03:01.352 --> 03:04.184
IT'S NOT ME.

03:04.184 --> 03:07.107
[ ELEVATOR DOOR CLOSES ]

03:07.107 --> 03:08.148
[ KEYBOARD CLACKS ]

03:08.148 --> 03:10.441
I'VE HACKED ALL OF KATE TAYLOR'S
PERSONNEL-REVIEW FILES

03:10.441 --> 03:11.862
IN THE FBI MAINFRAME.

03:11.862 --> 03:13.404
[ SIGHS ]
I MEAN, AFTER READING THIS,

03:13.404 --> 03:16.156
I WANT TO WRITE HER A LETTER
OF RECOMMENDATION MYSELF.

03:16.156 --> 03:18.909
TOP OF HER CLASS AT QUANTICO,
PROFICIENCY MEDALS

03:18.909 --> 03:20.281
IN HAND-TO-HAND COMBAT
AND FIREARMS.

03:20.281 --> 03:22.663
I EVEN CHECKED
HER FINANCES.

03:22.663 --> 03:24.495
SHE'S CLEAN AND...

03:24.495 --> 03:26.287
WELL-DIVERSIFIED,
I MIGHT ADD.

03:26.287 --> 03:28.999
JUST MEANS SHE'S AS GOOD AS I AM
AT HIDING HER SECRETS.

03:28.999 --> 03:31.382
OR MAYBE IT MEANS
SHE'S NOT DIRTY.

03:31.382 --> 03:33.634
I ALREADY FEEL
DOUCHE-BAGGY ENOUGH

03:33.634 --> 03:34.715
AFTER WHAT I DID
TO LOUISE.

03:34.715 --> 03:36.136
SHE DID NOT DESERVE IT.

03:36.136 --> 03:38.259
I SURE AS HELL
AM NOT GONNA DO THE SAME THING

03:38.259 --> 03:39.760
TO A FEDERAL AGENT.

03:39.760 --> 03:41.432
THEY HOLD GRUDGES...

03:41.432 --> 03:43.103
AND ARREST WARRANTS.

03:43.103 --> 03:45.105
I TRUST MY INSTINCTS,
NOLAN.

03:45.105 --> 03:46.647
KATE HAD ACCESS
TO THE PRISONER

03:46.647 --> 03:48.269
WHO WAS MURDERED
AT THE POLICE STATION.

03:48.269 --> 03:50.020
I THINK
SHE WAS TYING UP LOOSE ENDS.

03:50.020 --> 03:53.063
FOR OUR FACELESS CRIME BOSS,
MALCOLM BLACK,

03:53.063 --> 03:56.156
WHO I CAN'T EVEN
FIND A PICTURE OF, BY THE WAY?

03:56.156 --> 03:59.530
RUMOR HAS IT THAT HE OPERATES
OUT OF A SECURE COMPOUND,

03:59.530 --> 04:02.162
BUT NOBODY KNOWS WHERE.

04:02.162 --> 04:03.324
DON'T DO THAT.

04:03.324 --> 04:06.036
THE TRACKING DEVICE
YOU PLANTED ON HIS THUG

04:06.036 --> 04:07.328
DIDN'T LEAD ANYWHERE?

04:07.328 --> 04:10.751
UH, YEAH, IT DID --
STRAIGHT TO A MORGUE IN DETROIT.

04:10.751 --> 04:14.174
ELIMINATING LOOSE ENDS SEEMS
TO BE MALCOLM'S GO-TO MOVE.

04:14.174 --> 04:17.428
THEN KATE TAYLOR REALLY IS
MY ONLY WAY TO FIND HIM.

04:17.428 --> 04:20.591
[ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYS ]

04:37.738 --> 04:39.199
[ BEEPING ]

05:01.261 --> 05:04.054
EMILY. HEY.
 HI.

05:04.054 --> 05:06.226
IT'S FUNNY
BUMPING INTO YOU HERE.

05:06.226 --> 05:09.059
I WAS DROPPING OFF SOME FILES
WITH AGENT TAYLOR.

05:09.059 --> 05:10.981
I WAS JUST CHECKING OUT
THE CONFERENCE ROOM

05:10.981 --> 05:12.142
FOR AN EVENT
THAT I'M PLANNING.

05:12.142 --> 05:14.194
OH, I THOUGHT MAYBE
YOU WERE CHECKING UP ON JACK.

05:14.194 --> 05:16.106
HIM AND KATE?

05:16.106 --> 05:17.438
YEAH,
EVERYBODY AT THE STATION

05:17.438 --> 05:20.401
HAS GOT A LITTLE POOL GOING
ON THOSE TWO.

05:20.401 --> 05:22.072
I'M S-SORRY.
I THOUGHT --

05:22.072 --> 05:25.536
I'M SO SORRY.
I GOT TO GO.

05:29.209 --> 05:31.622
[ BOTH PANTING ]

05:31.622 --> 05:34.835
AW!

05:34.835 --> 05:36.797
ANYONE EVER TELL YOU
TO LET THE GIRL WIN?

05:36.797 --> 05:38.629
THAT WOULD'VE JUST
PISSED YOU OFF MORE.
 [ SCOFFS ]

05:38.629 --> 05:40.721
NICE READ.

05:40.721 --> 05:43.964
WOULD'VE MADE
AN EXCELLENT PROFILER.

05:43.964 --> 05:46.176
SHUT UP.
 HMM.

05:46.176 --> 05:48.138
WHAT MADE YOU CHANGE JOBS,
ANYWAY?

05:48.138 --> 05:51.732
FIELDWORK'S
MORE SATISFYING.

05:51.732 --> 05:53.474
MM.

05:55.065 --> 05:58.188
I HATE
THAT I HAVE TO GO INTO WORK...

05:58.188 --> 06:00.360
ESPECIALLY
WITH YOU LEAVING.

06:00.360 --> 06:04.535
WELL, ACTUALLY, I DO HAVE
A FEW VACATION DAYS BANKED.

06:04.535 --> 06:06.987
[ Laughing ] DON'T...

06:06.987 --> 06:07.988
DON'T GET COCKY, PORTER.
 MM.

06:07.988 --> 06:09.700
NOT EVERYTHING'S ABOUT YOU.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

06:09.700 --> 06:10.991
WELL, YOU KEEP
TELLING YOURSELF THAT.

06:10.991 --> 06:11.992
HMM.

06:11.992 --> 06:13.994
SINCE YOU ARE STAYING,
COME WITH ME

06:13.994 --> 06:17.207
TO THE REOPENING
OF NOLAN'S YACHT CLUB TONIGHT.

06:17.207 --> 06:18.378
OH.
THAT'S RIGHT.

06:18.378 --> 06:21.502
YOU'RE THE ROOKIE WHO KNOWS
EVERYONE WHO'S ANYONE.

06:21.502 --> 06:22.673
[ SIGHS ]

06:22.673 --> 06:24.595
NOLAN ROSS,
DAVID CLARKE, EMILY THORNE.

06:24.595 --> 06:25.806
SO,
IS THAT A YES?

06:25.806 --> 06:27.057
MM.

06:27.057 --> 06:28.348
I HAVE TO SEE
WHO RSVPs FIRST.

06:28.348 --> 06:30.771
YOU'RE GONNA FIT
RIGHT IN.

06:30.771 --> 06:32.272
[ CHUCKLES, SIGHS ]

06:34.354 --> 06:36.937
[ SIGHS ]

06:50.451 --> 06:51.452
♪ THERE WILL BE ANGELS,
THERE WILL BE DEVILS ♪

06:51.452 --> 06:53.874
♪ I WILL BE IN BETWEEN ♪

06:53.874 --> 06:56.126
♪ BUT I CROSS THAT LINE ♪
 AHOY!

06:56.126 --> 06:57.377
♪ SOME OF THE TIME ♪

06:57.377 --> 06:59.379
PERMISSION
TO COME ABOARD?

06:59.379 --> 07:03.213
SHARKS BELONG IN THE WATER,
NOT ON MY DECK.

07:03.213 --> 07:07.007
THOUGH, YOU'RE MORE
OF A BOTTOM-FEEDER, AREN'T YOU?

07:07.007 --> 07:08.428
♪ IF IT'S GONNA BURN, HONEY,
YOU WILL YOU LEARN ♪

07:08.428 --> 07:11.311
LOUISE, I FEEL AWFUL
THAT I HELPED MARGAUX

07:11.311 --> 07:12.683
WITH THAT HIT JOB.

07:12.683 --> 07:15.185
I ASKED HER
TO KILL THE STORY.

07:15.185 --> 07:17.518
♪ I WANT YOU TO WANT ME ♪
 SHE WOULDN'T.
I AM TRULY SORRY.

07:17.518 --> 07:19.520
♪ I WANT YOU TO WANT ME ♪
 MM.

07:19.520 --> 07:21.652
SO YOU SAID
IN YOUR E-MAILS...

07:21.652 --> 07:24.064
♪ I WANT YOU TO WANT ME ♪
 ...AND TEXTS.

07:24.064 --> 07:27.908
♪ I WANT YOU TO WANT ME ♪
 YOU ARE PERSISTENT.
I'LL GIVE YOU THAT.

07:27.908 --> 07:30.991
I EVEN LEFT YOU A VOICEMAIL,
FOR GOD SAKES.

07:30.991 --> 07:31.992
HMM.

07:31.992 --> 07:33.874
LOUISE, DON'T GO.

07:33.874 --> 07:37.077
LET ME HELP YOU PUT THAT STORY
IN YOUR REARVIEW.

07:37.077 --> 07:39.129
NOW, ARE YOU TRYING
TO ASSUAGE YOUR GUILT?

07:39.129 --> 07:42.002
'CAUSE IF SO...
CARRY ON.

07:42.002 --> 07:43.463
♪ THERE WILL BE LIGHT,
THERE WILL BE DARKNESS ♪

07:43.463 --> 07:47.588
WELL, LET'S GIVE THOSE VULTURES
SOMETHING ELSE TO TALK ABOUT.

07:47.588 --> 07:50.090
AFTER ALL, WE'RE BOTH FIXTURES
OF THE TABLOIDS.

07:50.090 --> 07:53.263
CAN YOU IMAGINE
THE HEADLINES WE WOULD CAUSE

07:53.263 --> 07:56.266
IF YOU CO-HOSTED MY EVENT
WITH ME TONIGHT?

07:56.266 --> 08:00.771
WE WOULD BE LIKE
THE WONDER TWINS OF GOSSIP.

08:00.771 --> 08:02.102
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

08:02.102 --> 08:03.403
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

08:03.403 --> 08:06.196
I'LL SAY,
"WONDER TWINS, ACTIVATE."

08:06.196 --> 08:07.197
PHEW!

08:07.197 --> 08:08.989
FORM OF
"PARTY OF THE SUMMER."

08:08.989 --> 08:10.571
♪ I WANT YOU TO WANT ME ♪
 [ CLICKS TONGUE ]

08:10.571 --> 08:11.912
[ LAUGHS ]

08:11.912 --> 08:13.704
[ BALL THUDS ]

08:33.183 --> 08:35.095
I'VE CALLED IN
A FAVOR.

08:35.095 --> 08:36.847
THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY
HAS AGREED

08:36.847 --> 08:38.808
TO REMOVE YOU
FROM THE WITNESS LIST.

08:38.808 --> 08:40.981
YOU WON'T HAVE TO TESTIFY
AT THE TRIAL.

08:40.981 --> 08:42.943
GINA WAS ASSAULTED
AT MY PARTY, DAD.

08:42.943 --> 08:44.605
SHE NEEDS ALL THE HELP
SHE CAN GET.

08:44.605 --> 08:46.446
YOU KNOW THE DEFENSE
WILL DESTROY HER
CHARACTER ON THE STAND.

08:46.446 --> 08:49.650
WELL...WITH GOOD REASON.

08:49.650 --> 08:51.111
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:51.111 --> 08:53.033
WHY DO YOU THINK
A GIRL FROM ROCKPORT

08:53.033 --> 08:54.955
WAS EVEN AT YOUR PARTY
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

08:54.955 --> 08:56.536
THIS IS A SHAKEDOWN
OF YOUR FRIEND.

08:56.536 --> 08:58.118
DREW ANDERSON'S
NO FRIEND OF MINE.

08:58.118 --> 09:00.330
ANDREW IS
A FRATERNITY BROTHER,

09:00.330 --> 09:02.332
WHICH MIGHT AS WELL
BE BLOOD.

09:02.332 --> 09:05.005
HE TOOK ADVANTAGE OF HER, DAD,
AND BRAGGED ABOUT IT LATER.

09:05.005 --> 09:07.047
I HAVE TO TESTIFY.

09:07.047 --> 09:10.090
DANIEL, YOUR CLASSMATE
HAS A POWERFUL FATHER

09:10.090 --> 09:12.092
WITH
EQUALLY POWERFUL FRIENDS.

09:12.092 --> 09:14.595
I'M HOPING
THAT YOU CAN RECOGNIZE

09:14.595 --> 09:17.848
HOW THAT WORKS FOR YOU
RATHER THAN AGAINST YOU.

09:17.848 --> 09:21.061
IF YOU COULD
DEFEND THIS GIRL

09:21.061 --> 09:22.773
WITHOUT JEOPARDIZING
YOUR OWN FUTURE,

09:22.773 --> 09:24.444
I MIGHT EVEN ENCOURAGE YOU
TO DO SO,

09:24.444 --> 09:26.026
BUT THAT IS NOT
THE CASE.

09:26.026 --> 09:28.318
WHY IS MY FUTURE
MORE IMPORTANT THAN HERS?

09:32.452 --> 09:35.495
I ONCE ASKED MYSELF
THE SAME QUESTION.

09:38.078 --> 09:40.831
I'LL TELL YOU
WHAT YOUR GRANDFATHER TAUGHT ME.

09:40.831 --> 09:46.546
THIS WORLD THAT WE'VE CREATED
IS MADE UP OF GODS AND INSECTS.

09:46.546 --> 09:49.589
AND IT'S NOT FAIR,
BUT THAT IS THE REALITY.

09:49.589 --> 09:53.383
DON'T CONCERN YOURSELF WITH
THE WELL-BEING OF ANTS, SON.

09:53.383 --> 09:57.848
IF YOU CAN SEE LIFE
THROUGH THAT LENS,

09:57.848 --> 10:01.982
YOUR CHOICES WILL BECOME
SIMPLER, EASIER TO MAKE...

10:04.224 --> 10:06.186
...AND LIVE WITH.

10:11.992 --> 10:14.324
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

10:14.324 --> 10:16.036
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
MR. GRAYSON?

10:16.036 --> 10:20.080
IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN GET YOU?

10:20.080 --> 10:24.204
NO, I'M FINE.

10:24.204 --> 10:28.168
ACTUALLY, I HAVE SOME, UH --
I HAVE ITEMS IN STORAGE.

10:28.168 --> 10:31.211
CAN YOU BRING THEM OUT
TO MY ROOM?

10:33.053 --> 10:34.344
JACK.
 [ DOOR CLOSES ]

10:34.344 --> 10:35.595
IS IT TRUE?

10:35.595 --> 10:38.258
ARE YOU SEEING
KATE TAYLOR?

10:38.258 --> 10:41.141
HOW DID YOU EVEN KNOW
ABOUT THAT?

10:41.141 --> 10:43.023
YOU SPYING ON ME
OR HER?

10:43.023 --> 10:44.815
LOOK,
I THINK SHE WAS INVOLVED

10:44.815 --> 10:46.356
WITH THE ATTACKS
ON MY FATHER.

10:46.356 --> 10:47.978
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

10:47.978 --> 10:48.979
MY FATHER LIED.

10:48.979 --> 10:50.400
CONRAD DIDN'T
HOLD HIM CAPTIVE.

10:50.400 --> 10:52.152
IT WAS A MAN
NAMED MALCOLM BLACK.

10:52.152 --> 10:53.774
I BELIEVE THAT KATE
IS HIS OPERATIVE.

10:53.774 --> 10:55.365
SHE'S A FEDERAL AGENT.

10:55.365 --> 10:57.117
WHO CHOSE A ROOKIE
TO WORK HER CASE --

10:57.117 --> 10:58.869
THE SON-IN-LAW OF DAVID CLARKE,
HER TARGET.

10:58.869 --> 11:01.161
THE CASE IS CLOSED,
EMS.

11:01.161 --> 11:03.163
KATE'S GOING BACK
TO D.C.

11:03.163 --> 11:05.665
THEN I BET SHE'LL FIND
A REASON TO STAY.

11:08.588 --> 11:11.291
LOOK, IF I'M RIGHT ABOUT HER,
SHE'S DANGEROUS.

11:11.291 --> 11:15.095
I HAD TO WARN YOU.
I...

11:15.095 --> 11:17.557
I COULDN'T LIVE WITH MYSELF
IF SOMETHING HAPPENED TO YOU.

11:22.853 --> 11:26.436
A LONG WAY FROM THE PRISON YARD,
HUH, KERN?

11:26.436 --> 11:27.938
LONGER FOR YOU.

11:27.938 --> 11:29.109
I GOT PAROLED.

11:29.109 --> 11:31.151
YOU WERE RESURRECTED.

11:31.151 --> 11:32.192
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

11:32.192 --> 11:33.443
YEAH,
I SUPPOSE SO.

11:33.443 --> 11:34.574
DO YOU HAVE IT?

11:34.574 --> 11:37.317
I'LL ALWAYS COME THROUGH
FOR MY OLD CELLMATE.

11:37.317 --> 11:39.990
BUT YOUR REQUEST
DID CATCH ME BY SURPRISE.

11:39.990 --> 11:41.661
THIS WAS NEVER
YOUR STYLE.

11:41.661 --> 11:44.204
I'M NOT
THE SAME MAN ANYMORE.

11:44.204 --> 11:45.455
AND I'M NOT JUDGING.

11:45.455 --> 11:47.918
AFTER WHAT THEY DID,
THEY DESERVE FAR WORSE.

11:47.918 --> 11:50.540
ATROPA BELLADONNA.

11:50.540 --> 11:52.502
WILL TAKE DOWN
A 200-POUND MAN.

11:52.502 --> 11:55.335
WILL LOOK LIKE A STROKE --
BASICALLY UNTRACEABLE.

11:57.097 --> 11:58.718
PERFECT.

11:58.718 --> 12:00.550
JUST BE SURE
YOU HAVE NO DOUBTS.

12:00.550 --> 12:01.892
THERE'S NO TURNING BACK.

12:09.850 --> 12:12.232
[ GASPS ]
 SORRY TO STARTLE YOU,
MRS. GRAYSON.

12:12.232 --> 12:13.653
AGENT TAYLOR
FROM THE FBI.

12:13.653 --> 12:15.525
WE MET THE OTHER DAY
AT THE HOSPITAL.

12:15.525 --> 12:16.987
HAD A FEW
FOLLOW-UP QUESTIONS

12:16.987 --> 12:18.568
REGARDING THE ATTACKS
ON MR. CLARKE.

12:18.568 --> 12:19.569
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:19.569 --> 12:20.991
I'M LATE FOR AN APPOINTMENT
IN THE CITY,

12:20.991 --> 12:23.283
AND I ALREADY TOLD INVESTIGATORS
THAT I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING.

12:23.283 --> 12:27.497
A NEW PIECE OF EVIDENCE
CAME ACROSS MY DESK, AND...

12:27.497 --> 12:30.000
I WANTED TO GET YOUR THOUGHTS
ON IT.

12:37.637 --> 12:39.179
I WAS ABLE TO TRACE
THIS PHOTOGRAPH BACK TO YOU.

12:39.179 --> 12:40.220
MIND EXPLAINING
THE MESSAGE?

12:40.220 --> 12:41.972
I DIDN'T SEND IT.

12:41.972 --> 12:43.844
AND I QUESTION
HOW YOU WOULD PROVE THAT I DID.

12:43.844 --> 12:46.436
WE'RE THE FBI, MRS. GRAYSON.
THAT'S WHAT WE DO.

12:46.436 --> 12:48.058
SO,
WHY DON'T YOU COOPERATE

12:48.058 --> 12:51.021
AND TELL ME HOW EMILY THORNE
IS INVOLVED IN ALL THIS?

12:51.021 --> 12:53.023
THAT'S A BUSH-LEAGUE QUESTION,
AGENT TAYLOR.

12:53.023 --> 12:55.025
I THOUGHT I WAS DEALING
WITH A PROFESSIONAL.

12:56.446 --> 12:58.108
FINE.

12:58.108 --> 13:00.030
EMILY THORNE
WAS CELLMATES

13:00.030 --> 13:01.902
WITH DAVID CLARKE'S DAUGHTER,
AMANDA.

13:01.902 --> 13:03.073
AND WHAT
DOES THAT TELL YOU?

13:03.073 --> 13:05.996
THAT THEY SHARED
A SPECIAL BOND.

13:05.996 --> 13:08.498
OH, "SPECIAL" WOULDN'T EVEN
BEGIN TO COVER IT.

13:08.498 --> 13:10.040
HOW SO?

13:10.040 --> 13:12.042
EMILY WILL DO ANYTHING
FOR DAVID,

13:12.042 --> 13:15.335
INCLUDING ERASING
HIS DEBTS.

13:16.626 --> 13:18.718
WHICH,
JUDGING BY YOUR REACTION,

13:18.718 --> 13:20.680
MIGHT PROVE INTERESTING
TO YOUR EMPLOYER.

13:20.680 --> 13:22.012
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:22.012 --> 13:24.304
I WORK FOR THE UNITED STATES
TAXPAYERS, MRS. GRAYSON.

13:24.304 --> 13:25.475
AH.

13:25.475 --> 13:28.428
AND I DO SO MISS
MY DEARLY DEPARTED HUSBAND.

13:28.428 --> 13:31.231
NOW, ONLY ONE OF THOSE
STATEMENTS CAN BE VERIFIED.

13:31.231 --> 13:33.603
SHALL I CALL QUANTICO
AND SHARE MY THEORIES

13:33.603 --> 13:35.735
ABOUT YOUR
EXTRACURRICULAR ACTIVITIES?

13:35.735 --> 13:39.109
WHAT IS IT YOU WANT?

13:39.109 --> 13:41.992
JUST FOR DAVID AND I
TO HAVE THE RELATIONSHIP

13:41.992 --> 13:45.785
WE WERE DENIED YEARS AGO,
FREE FROM ANYONE'S INTERFERENCE.

13:45.785 --> 13:50.210
WELL, MS. THORNE
IS A VERY WEALTHY GIRL,

13:50.210 --> 13:52.002
BUT I DON'T SEE WHY
SHE WOULD GO TO SUCH EXTREMES

13:52.002 --> 13:53.413
TO HELP DAVID CLARKE.

13:53.413 --> 13:54.875
WHAT'S THE CONNECTION?

13:54.875 --> 13:57.047
YOU'RE THE FBI.
FIGURE IT OUT.

13:57.047 --> 14:02.092
AND ONCE YOU DO, TAKE YOUR MONEY
AND LEAVE US THE HELL ALONE.

14:02.092 --> 14:04.965
[ SEA GULLS CRYING ]

14:04.965 --> 14:07.177
HEY.

14:07.177 --> 14:08.268
HEY.

14:08.268 --> 14:10.430
SO, UH,
I AM RUNNING KATE'S PRINTS

14:10.430 --> 14:12.232
THROUGH
A DATA-MINING PROGRAM.

14:12.232 --> 14:14.234
IF SHE'S HIDING SOMETHING,
I'LL FIND IT,

14:14.234 --> 14:15.315
BUT IT'S GONNA
TAKE AWHILE.

14:15.315 --> 14:17.147
[ SIGHS ] WHAT ABOUT THE FEED
FROM THE ROOM?

14:17.147 --> 14:18.688
ANYTHING INTERESTING?

14:18.688 --> 14:21.191
WELL, FOR STARTERS,
SHE'S A TOTAL SLOB,

14:21.191 --> 14:23.403
BUT I DID
FIND SOMETHING USEFUL

14:23.403 --> 14:27.037
WHILE YOU WERE ENGAGED
IN YOUR TêTE-à-JACK.

14:27.037 --> 14:30.120
SHE'S JUST
TEXTING SOMEONE.

14:30.120 --> 14:31.581
Nolan: UH-HUH.

14:31.581 --> 14:33.583
ON A PHONE
THAT'S IN DIRECT VIOLATION

14:33.583 --> 14:36.166
OF ANTI-CORRUPTION
PROTOCOL.

14:36.166 --> 14:39.379
ALL AGENTS ARE SUPPOSED TO
REGISTER THEIR SECONDARY PHONES,

14:39.379 --> 14:40.630
BUT KATE NEVER DID.

14:40.630 --> 14:43.093
SHE'S ON A SATCOM
WITH A DIGITAL SCRAMBLER,

14:43.093 --> 14:44.504
WHICH IS KIND OF IDEAL

14:44.504 --> 14:46.676
FOR STAYING IN TOUCH
WITH PARANOID SHUT-INS.

14:46.676 --> 14:48.808
IF I GET THE PHONE,
CAN YOU TRACE THE TEXT?

14:48.808 --> 14:50.140
[ SCOFFS ]

14:50.140 --> 14:53.143
I CAN PINPOINT MALCOLM BLACK
TO A 10-FOOT RADIUS.

14:53.143 --> 14:55.225
DID JACK RSVP
TO YOUR PARTY?

14:55.225 --> 14:57.147
HE DID -- PLUS ONE.

14:57.147 --> 14:59.649
BUT, EMS,
DON'T EVEN THINK

14:59.649 --> 15:02.232
OF TURNING MY CLUB INTO
YOUR OWN PERSONAL BATTLEFIELD.

15:02.232 --> 15:04.194
I JUST PAID
FOR NEW UNIFORMS.

15:04.194 --> 15:05.695
IF EVERYTHING
GOES RIGHT,

15:05.695 --> 15:07.737
KATE WON'T EVEN KNOW
I'M ON TO HER.

15:07.737 --> 15:09.829
HMM. WHEN DOES ANYTHING
EVER GO RIGHT

15:09.829 --> 15:12.162
FOR THE HOST
OF A HAMPTONS' PARTY...

15:12.162 --> 15:13.793
with you
on the guest list?

15:13.793 --> 15:16.796
I HEARD THAT.

15:16.796 --> 15:18.248
'COURSE YOU DID.

15:18.248 --> 15:19.839
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

15:19.839 --> 15:21.091
WELL,
THE COPY IS GOOD,

15:21.091 --> 15:22.542
BUT I'D LIKE
TO USE THE PHOTO

15:22.542 --> 15:24.344
OF THE GRAYSON GLOBAL RETREAT
IN HAWAII.

15:24.344 --> 15:26.176
IT'S A BETTER SHOT
OF DAVID.

15:27.968 --> 15:30.310
MARGAUX?

15:30.310 --> 15:32.182
YES.

15:32.182 --> 15:33.893
WHAT'S WRONG?

15:36.016 --> 15:38.688
WAS CONRAD ALWAYS
LIKE HE WAS AT THE END?

15:38.688 --> 15:42.612
WAS HE EVER...
DIFFERENT?

15:42.612 --> 15:44.484
WHEN HE WAS YOUNG.

15:44.484 --> 15:46.616
HE WASN'T KIND,

15:46.616 --> 15:50.530
BUT HE WASN'T CRUEL...THEN.

15:50.530 --> 15:52.952
WHAT CHANGED HIM?

15:52.952 --> 15:55.575
OH, I SUPPOSE
HE HAD A LOT TO PROVE.

15:55.575 --> 15:58.038
GROWING UP UNDER THE SHADOW
OF A POWERFUL FATHER

15:58.038 --> 16:00.080
IS A TERRIBLE BURDEN
FOR A CHILD --

16:00.080 --> 16:01.131
SOMETHING YOU KNOW WELL.

16:01.131 --> 16:02.542
MM-HMM.

16:02.542 --> 16:05.345
THIS ISN'T ABOUT CONRAD,
IS IT?

16:05.345 --> 16:07.587
THIS IS ABOUT
YOU AND DANIEL.

16:10.010 --> 16:11.351
I'M PREGNANT.

16:11.351 --> 16:13.803
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:15.975 --> 16:18.188
DOES HE KNOW?

16:21.101 --> 16:23.023
BUT YOU'RE THINKING
OF GOING IT ALONE?

16:23.023 --> 16:27.277
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I'M EVEN CONSIDERING IT.

16:27.277 --> 16:30.490
I WAS SO LONELY
AS A CHILD.

16:30.490 --> 16:32.612
MY FATHER
WAS NEVER HOME.

16:32.612 --> 16:35.075
ALWAYS CAME SECOND
TO HIS WORK.

16:35.075 --> 16:38.038
THEN WHY
PUSH DANIEL AWAY?

16:39.959 --> 16:43.213
HE WAS ONCE
FULL OF HOPE...

16:43.213 --> 16:45.925
A BEAUTIFUL YOUNG MAN.

16:45.925 --> 16:50.130
BUT SOMETHING CHANGED
IN HIM.

16:50.130 --> 16:55.345
AND NOW THERE'S SO MUCH MORE
AT STAKE.

16:55.345 --> 17:00.640
YOU KNOW, I WAS ONCE FACED
WITH RAISING A BABY ALONE.

17:00.640 --> 17:02.312
BUT I COULDN'T.

17:02.312 --> 17:06.025
I WAS 16 YEARS OLD,
AND OUR CIRCUMSTANCES WERE DIRE.

17:06.025 --> 17:07.857
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

17:07.857 --> 17:10.029
YOUR SITUATION
IS DIFFERENT.

17:10.029 --> 17:13.413
BUT NO MATTER
HOW CAPABLE A MOTHER,

17:13.413 --> 17:16.205
A CHILD
DESERVES A FATHER.

17:18.078 --> 17:21.421
EVEN ONE LIKE HIM?

17:24.002 --> 17:27.087
DANIEL'S NOT CONRAD,
AND I KNOW THE DIFFERENCE.

17:27.087 --> 17:28.968
WHICH IS WHY I ALSO KNOW

17:28.968 --> 17:31.551
THAT THE GOOD MAN YOU NEED
IS STILL THERE.

17:31.551 --> 17:33.933
DANIEL LOVES YOU.

17:40.230 --> 17:42.232
BUT WHAT IF
I DON'T LOVE HIM ANYMORE?

17:42.232 --> 17:45.185
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:45.185 --> 17:47.237
YOUR TEARS
SUGGEST OTHERWISE.

17:49.689 --> 17:51.030
[ SIGHS ]

17:51.030 --> 17:52.992
♪ BANG BANG INTO THE ROOM ♪
 Nolan: WELL, MY, MY.

17:52.992 --> 17:55.615
♪ BANG BANG ALL OVER YOU ♪
 SOUTHERN GIRLS CERTAINLY DO KNOW
HOW TO PUT ON A HOOTENANNY.

17:55.615 --> 17:57.497
♪ I'LL LET YOU HAVE IT ♪
 DON'T USE THAT WORD.
 WHY?

17:57.497 --> 17:59.869
♪ WAIT A MINUTE,
LET ME TAKE YOU THERE ♪
 'CAUSE YOU CAN'T
PULL IT OFF.

17:59.869 --> 18:01.661
[ SIGHS ] OH.

18:01.661 --> 18:04.124
♪ WAIT A MINUTE TILL YA ♪
 WELL, YOU'RE CERTAINLY RIGHT
ABOUT ONE THING --

18:04.124 --> 18:05.835
WE ARE
THE COUPLE OF THE MOMENT.
 OH, YES.

18:05.835 --> 18:07.207
♪ I KNOW YOU WANT IT ♪

18:07.207 --> 18:08.628
♪ BACK, BACKSEAT OF MY CAR ♪

18:08.628 --> 18:10.210
LoLan IS TRENDING.
 [ GASPS ]

18:10.210 --> 18:12.091
♪ WAIT A MINUTE,
LET ME TAKE YOU THERE ♪

18:12.091 --> 18:14.053
OKAY, WE HAVE TO THANK OUR FANS
WITH A SELFIE.

18:14.053 --> 18:15.765
♪ WAIT A MINUTE TILL YA ♪
 WHAT'S YOUR GOOD SIDE?

18:15.765 --> 18:17.307
UH, SAME AS YOU --
ALL OF THEM.

18:17.307 --> 18:18.888
♪ SHE MIGHT OF LET
YOU HOLD HER HAND IN SCHOOL ♪
 [ GIGGLES ]

18:18.888 --> 18:20.890
♪ BUT I'M GONNA SHOW YOU
HOW TO GRADUATE ♪

18:20.890 --> 18:23.483
TAG ME -- NolMan 88.

18:23.483 --> 18:26.025
♪ NO, I DON'T NEED TO HEAR YOU
TALK THE TALK ♪
 WHY 88?

18:26.025 --> 18:29.439
♪ JUST COME AND SHOW ME
WHAT YOUR MAMA GAVE ♪
 WELL, SOME DETAILS OF MY PRIVATE
LIFE I DON'T MAKE PUBLIC.

18:29.439 --> 18:32.071
♪ YOU'VE GOT A VERY BIG SHH ♪

18:32.071 --> 18:34.073
DON'T TURN AROUND.

18:34.073 --> 18:36.196
I'M SORRY
THAT I KEPT YOU IN THE DARK.

18:36.196 --> 18:38.238
I KNOW HOW HARD
THAT'S BEEN FOR YOU.

18:38.238 --> 18:40.790
I CAN HANDLE MYSELF.

18:40.790 --> 18:42.041
I KNOW.

18:42.041 --> 18:45.665
BUT I CAN'T HAVE YOU INVOLVED
IN WHAT HAPPENS NEXT.

18:45.665 --> 18:47.086
David: WHEN YOU HEAR
THERE'S TROUBLE,

18:47.086 --> 18:48.588
DO NOT COME RUNNING.

18:48.588 --> 18:50.840
IT'S ALL PART
OF A LARGER PLAN.

18:50.840 --> 18:54.053
DON'T GO AFTER MALCOLM BLACK
ON YOUR OWN, PLEASE.

18:54.053 --> 18:55.215
LET ME HELP YOU.

19:05.525 --> 19:08.938
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

19:08.938 --> 19:10.069
DID MY FATHER
MENTION ANYTHING

19:10.069 --> 19:11.481
ABOUT GOING AFTER
MALCOLM BLACK?

19:11.481 --> 19:12.482
NO, NOTHING.

19:12.482 --> 19:13.773
NOLAN, IF HE DID,
TELL ME.

19:13.773 --> 19:16.115
EMS, I SWEAR
HE DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING.

19:16.115 --> 19:18.948
THEN HE REALLY IS
WORKING ALONE.

19:18.948 --> 19:20.870
I NEED TO GET
TO MALCOLM FIRST.

19:20.870 --> 19:22.782
WELL, YOUR BEST
AND ONLY OPTION

19:22.782 --> 19:24.954
JUST WALKED
THROUGH THE FRONT DOOR.

19:24.954 --> 19:28.588
♪ ANYONE AT ALL, BABY, WHAT
YOU DID, IT AIN'T TOO EASY ♪

19:28.588 --> 19:30.290
JACK.

19:30.290 --> 19:31.291
YOU MADE IT.

19:31.291 --> 19:34.093
EMILY.
THIS IS KATE TAYLOR.

19:34.093 --> 19:35.385
I WAS HOPING
TO MEET YOU.

19:35.385 --> 19:37.217
THINK I...
SAW YOU AT THE HOSPITAL.

19:37.217 --> 19:39.469
AND, UH,
AT THE POLICE STATION.
 MM-HMM.

19:39.469 --> 19:42.181
WE'RE LIKE TWO SHIPS
THAT KEEP PASSING IN THE NIGHT.

19:42.181 --> 19:43.893
OH, AT LEAST WE'RE NOT
CRASHING INTO EACH OTHER.

19:43.893 --> 19:45.265
AH, WELL,
THE NIGHT IS STILL YOUNG.

19:45.265 --> 19:49.979
JACK, WHO IS YOUR LOVELY DAMSEL
IN THIS STUNNING DRESS?

19:49.979 --> 19:50.980
[ GASPS ]
 OH, WHOOPS.

19:50.980 --> 19:52.191
[ KATE CHUCKLES ]

19:52.191 --> 19:55.815
NOTHING WORSE THAN A PARTY FOUL
FROM HE WHO THROWS THE PARTY.

19:55.815 --> 19:57.777
I'VE BEEN HIT WITH WORSE.
UH, NAME'S KATE.

19:57.777 --> 20:00.159
NOLAN ROSS.
UH, BUT YOU KNEW THAT.

20:00.159 --> 20:02.372
UH, AND I AM SO SORRY
ABOUT THE DRESS.

20:02.372 --> 20:04.033
UM,
THAT ONE NOTWITHSTANDING,

20:04.033 --> 20:06.586
REST OF THE DRINKS TONIGHT
ON ME.

20:06.586 --> 20:07.667
DO YOU HAVE A --

20:07.667 --> 20:09.038
LADIES --
AROUND THE CORNER.

20:09.038 --> 20:10.039
THANKS.

20:12.001 --> 20:14.213
YOU OKAY?

20:14.213 --> 20:16.045
IF SHE'S CORRUPT,
I WANT TO KNOW.

20:16.045 --> 20:17.837
IF SHE'S NOT,
I WANT AN APOLOGY.

20:28.107 --> 20:30.900
Daniel:
 "DEAR DAD, MY WHOLE LIFE,

20:30.900 --> 20:33.273
"I'VE BEEN TOLD
I WAS DESTINED FOR GREATNESS

20:33.273 --> 20:35.315
BASED SOLELY
ON THE VIRTUE OF MY NAME."

20:35.315 --> 20:36.316
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

20:58.177 --> 20:59.929
I THOUGHT
YOU COULD USE THIS.

20:59.929 --> 21:01.971
I'VE SPILLED
MY FAIR SHARE OF DRINKS.

21:01.971 --> 21:09.148
[ CHUCKLES ]
 THANKS.

21:09.148 --> 21:11.351
JACK'S SAID SOME NICE THINGS
ABOUT YOU.

21:11.351 --> 21:14.103
REALLY?
 IS THAT SURPRISING?

21:14.103 --> 21:16.396
OH, WE'RE JUST...
HAVING A LITTLE FUN.

21:16.396 --> 21:17.487
NOTHING SERIOUS.

21:17.487 --> 21:18.948
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

21:18.948 --> 21:21.701
WELL, THAT'S AS GOOD
AS IT'S GONNA GET.

21:21.701 --> 21:22.952
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

21:22.952 --> 21:25.164
[ SIGHS ]

21:25.164 --> 21:26.866
THANKS FOR THE ASSIST.

21:26.866 --> 21:28.828
OF COURSE.

21:28.828 --> 21:32.041
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

21:39.008 --> 21:40.840
[ FUTURE ISLANDS' "SEASONS
(WAITING ON YOU)" PLAYS ]

21:40.840 --> 21:42.882
♪ SEASONS CHANGE ♪

21:42.882 --> 21:46.386
♪ AND I TRIED HARD
JUST TO SOFTEN YOU ♪
 SCRAM.

21:46.386 --> 21:47.887
AW.

21:47.887 --> 21:50.560
HOW I ENJOY
TOYING WITH THE WEAKER SEX.

21:50.560 --> 21:54.354
UH, WELL, THAT INCLUDES ME, TOO,
DOESN'T IT?

21:54.354 --> 21:55.935
♪ SEASONS CHANGE ♪
 SEE, I JUST HEARD

21:55.935 --> 21:58.277
THAT YOU ARE HITTING THE OPEN
SEAS TOMORROW AFTER ALL.

21:58.277 --> 22:00.860
♪ BUT I'VE GROWN TIRED
OF TRYING TO CHANGE FOR YOU ♪

22:00.860 --> 22:03.202
THOUGHT WE WERE OKAY.

22:03.202 --> 22:05.365
[ SIGHS ] WE ARE.

22:07.036 --> 22:09.909
THINGS WILL NEVER BE OKAY
WITH ME AND MY BROTHER.

22:09.909 --> 22:12.041
SO THIS IS
 ABOUT THE ARTICLE.

22:12.041 --> 22:13.082
♪ I'VE BEEN WAITING ON YOU ♪
 MM.

22:13.082 --> 22:15.004
PARTICULARLY THE PASSAGE

22:15.004 --> 22:18.087
HINTING AT THE REAL STORY
BEHIND THE ELLISE FAMILY.

22:18.087 --> 22:21.300
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE BEEN WAITING
ON YOU ♪
 SEE, MY BROTHER
VALUES OUR SECRETS.

22:21.300 --> 22:23.963
HE'LL DO ANYTHING
TO KEEP THEM BURIED.

22:23.963 --> 22:26.175
I CANNOT
GO THROUGH THAT AGAIN.

22:26.175 --> 22:28.227
♪ I'VE BEEN WAITING ON YOU ♪

22:30.430 --> 22:32.732
I have to get
the hell away from him.

22:32.732 --> 22:36.275
RUNNING --
NOT THE ANSWER.

22:36.275 --> 22:40.860
THERE IS ANOTHER WAY
OUT OF THIS, LOUISE...

22:42.031 --> 22:46.245
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE BEEN WAITING
ON YOU ♪
 ...IF YOU'RE UP FOR IT.

22:49.038 --> 22:52.331
[ GIGGLES ]

22:52.331 --> 22:54.414
[ SLOW-TEMPO PIANO MUSIC PLAYS ]

22:54.414 --> 22:56.165
ENJOY.

23:01.210 --> 23:02.882
I WASN'T SURE
YOU'D COME.

23:02.882 --> 23:04.133
YEAH,
I WOULDN'T HAVE,

23:04.133 --> 23:06.135
EXCEPT YOU SAID
IT INVOLVED MARGAUX.

23:06.135 --> 23:07.266
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

23:07.266 --> 23:09.849
SHE TOLD ME, DANIEL,
AND I AM SO HAPPY FOR YOU.

23:09.849 --> 23:11.721
STOP. STOP IT.
 I'VE ALWAYS DREAMED
OF YOU AND MAR--

23:11.721 --> 23:13.222
STOP.
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

23:13.222 --> 23:14.854
YOU'RE TRYING
TO CONTROL THE SITUATION.

23:14.854 --> 23:16.436
I'M NOT.

23:16.436 --> 23:18.107
AND I RESENT
THE ACCUSATION.

23:18.107 --> 23:20.069
THIS IS ALWAYS --
THIS IS WHAT YOU DO.

23:20.069 --> 23:22.191
YOU ALWAYS DO THIS.
YOU...

23:25.154 --> 23:27.827
YESTERDAY,
I WOULD'VE FOUGHT WITH YOU,

23:27.827 --> 23:32.832
BUT I CAN'T KEEP REPEATING
THE SAME MISTAKES.

23:32.832 --> 23:34.293
I'M GONNA BE A FATHER.

23:34.293 --> 23:36.916
AND YOU'RE GOING TO BE
A GREAT ONE, DANIEL.

23:36.916 --> 23:38.207
NO, I DON'T KNOW.

23:38.207 --> 23:40.419
I THINK MARGAUX
WAS RIGHT.

23:40.419 --> 23:42.131
I'VE -- I'VE CHANGED.

23:42.131 --> 23:44.594
DANIEL.

23:44.594 --> 23:46.255
SHE'S ONLY REACTING
OUT OF FEAR.

23:46.255 --> 23:47.807
THAT'S ALL.

23:47.807 --> 23:51.140
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHAT I'VE
BEEN DOING FOR MOST OF MY LIFE.

23:51.140 --> 23:54.263
YOU KNOW, I WALKED AWAY
FROM SARA IN THAT ACCIDENT.

23:54.263 --> 23:57.436
I SIDED WITH DAD
WHEN YOU GAVE ME THAT EVIDENCE.

23:57.436 --> 24:00.229
I SHOT MY EX-WIFE.

24:00.229 --> 24:02.021
DON'T MAKE EXCUSES FOR HER,
DANIEL.

24:02.021 --> 24:03.693
SHE PUT YOU
THROUGH HELL.

24:03.693 --> 24:05.905
SHE FORCED US
TO FACE THE TRUTH.

24:05.905 --> 24:07.196
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:07.196 --> 24:08.828
I'M -- I'M GRATEFUL

24:08.828 --> 24:11.831
BECAUSE IT MEANS
I CAN'T HIDE FROM IT ANYMORE.

24:13.743 --> 24:15.204
YOU'VE SUFFERED,
AS WELL.

24:15.204 --> 24:18.998
MOM, WE HAVE TO STOP LYING
TO OURSELVES.

24:18.998 --> 24:21.000
LOOK AT WHAT YOU'RE DOING
TO DAVID.

24:21.000 --> 24:22.131
DOES HE KNOW
THE TRUTH?

24:22.131 --> 24:24.213
DOES HE HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT YOU DID TO HIM?

24:24.213 --> 24:26.926
NO.
OF COURSE NOT.

24:26.926 --> 24:29.138
NO, 'CAUSE YOU
MANIPULATED HIM INSTEAD.

24:29.138 --> 24:31.511
BECAUSE SURVIVING
IS ALL THAT MATTERS,

24:31.511 --> 24:33.052
JUST LIKE DAD SAID.

24:33.052 --> 24:35.184
BUT HE WAS WRONG.

24:35.184 --> 24:38.808
NO, SURVIVING'S NOT LIVING --
IT'S HIDING.

24:38.808 --> 24:40.019
YEAH,
WE THROW BIG PARTIES,

24:40.019 --> 24:42.361
GIVE OURSELVES AWARDS
TO COVER UP THE TRUTH.

24:42.361 --> 24:45.064
WE'RE NOT SPECIAL.

24:45.064 --> 24:47.446
WE'RE COWARDS.

24:49.448 --> 24:50.740
NOW,
IF I GET THE CHANCE,

24:50.740 --> 24:52.532
I'M TEACHING MY CHILD
TO BE BETTER THAN THAT.

24:54.574 --> 24:57.787
[ BILLS RUSTLE ]

24:57.787 --> 25:01.080
I'M DONE RUNNING.
[ SIGHS ]

25:01.080 --> 25:03.082
I HOPE YOU ARE, TOO.

25:13.933 --> 25:15.094
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

25:15.094 --> 25:17.136
YOU WOULD THINK THE FBI
WOULD TEACH THEIR AGENTS

25:17.136 --> 25:18.768
NOT TO LEAVE
THEIR BAGS UNATTENDED.

25:18.768 --> 25:21.641
SO,
WHAT'S NEXT?

25:21.641 --> 25:23.232
NOLAN PINPOINTS
MALCOLM'S LOCATION.

25:23.232 --> 25:25.605
JACK, YOU DISTRACT KATE
SO I CAN RETURN HER PHONE

25:25.605 --> 25:27.276
WITHOUT HER REALIZING
IT'S MISSING.

25:27.276 --> 25:30.910
THIS IS NOT HOW I EXPECTED
TO SPEND MY SUMMER.

25:30.910 --> 25:35.034
OKAY, HACKED,
SEALED, DELIVERED.

25:39.749 --> 25:43.212
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

25:43.212 --> 25:44.423
[ METAL CLINKS ]

25:44.423 --> 25:47.296
I THINK YOU HAVE
MY PHONE...AMANDA.

25:49.088 --> 25:50.469
IT WAS THE ONLY THING
THAT MADE SENSE.

25:50.469 --> 25:51.881
AND YOU'RE BETTER
THAN I THOUGHT.

25:51.881 --> 25:53.302
I DIDN'T EVEN NOTICE YOU
LIFT MY PHONE.

25:53.302 --> 25:55.474
YOU REALLY WANT
TO DO THIS HERE?

25:55.474 --> 25:57.597
I DIDN'T COME HERE
TO FIGHT.

25:57.597 --> 25:58.888
I NEED YOUR HELP.

25:58.888 --> 26:00.179
WHEN I FIGURED OUT
WHO YOU WERE,

26:00.179 --> 26:03.062
I REALIZED YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO TOOK DOWN CONRAD GRAYSON.

26:03.062 --> 26:04.143
SOMEONE HAD TO.

26:04.143 --> 26:06.565
NOW YOU HAVE TO DO THE SAME
TO MALCOLM.

26:06.565 --> 26:08.858
HE'S FORCING ME
TO WORK FOR HIM...

26:08.858 --> 26:12.992
JUST LIKE HE DID WITH YOUR
FATHER, AND HE HAS MY MOTHER.

26:12.992 --> 26:16.155
WHY SHOULD I
BELIEVE YOU?

26:16.155 --> 26:20.199
WHAT WOULD I POSSIBLY HAVE
TO GAIN BY OUTING MYSELF TO YOU?

26:20.199 --> 26:21.460
I'M DESPERATE.

26:21.460 --> 26:23.162
YOU'RE BEING WATCHED?

26:23.162 --> 26:25.755
ALWAYS.

26:25.755 --> 26:29.839
WHY DON'T WE SLIP AWAY...
SOMEWHERE SAFE?

26:29.839 --> 26:31.130
THEN I'LL TELL YOU

26:31.130 --> 26:34.093
EXACTLY HOW WE SAVE YOUR FATHER
AND MY MOTHER.

26:34.093 --> 26:35.134
DO WE HAVE A DEAL?

26:40.219 --> 26:42.521
MY HOUSE.
30 MINUTES.

26:47.987 --> 26:50.279
I WAS STARTING
TO GET WORRIED.

26:50.279 --> 26:52.822
I WAS IN THE CITY
WITH DANIEL.

26:52.822 --> 26:56.495
HE, UH --
HE SEEMED DIFFERENT TODAY,

26:56.495 --> 26:58.698
LIKE I'D NEVER SEEN HIM
BEFORE.

26:58.698 --> 27:01.120
I WAS PROUD OF HIM.

27:01.120 --> 27:03.292
I'M GLAD.

27:03.292 --> 27:05.084
DID YOU DO
WHAT YOU NEEDED TODAY?

27:05.084 --> 27:07.046
YES.
IT'S ALL TAKEN CARE OF.

27:11.210 --> 27:13.092
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE FINE.

27:33.152 --> 27:36.155
[ WAVES CRASHING ]

27:50.750 --> 27:52.792
WHY IS MY FUTURE
MORE IMPORTANT THAN HERS?

28:02.301 --> 28:06.015
I RECEIVED
YOUR LETTER...

28:06.015 --> 28:08.187
A BEAUTIFULLY PENNED
SUICIDE NOTE.

28:08.187 --> 28:10.519
PLEASE DON'T TRY
TO STOP ME, DAD.

28:10.519 --> 28:14.023
I WON'T. I GET IT.

28:14.023 --> 28:16.615
YOU'RE A MAN NOW,

28:16.615 --> 28:20.319
FACING THE FIRST REAL CHOICE
OF YOUR ADULT LIFE.

28:20.319 --> 28:24.163
I SIMPLY WANT YOU TO BE AWARE
OF ITS IMPLICATIONS.

28:24.163 --> 28:27.706
SO, DO YOU REMEMBER
THE FABLE OF MOMUS?

28:27.706 --> 28:32.251
YEAH, THE GOD OF...
WRITERS AND POETS.

28:32.251 --> 28:35.714
HE CRITICIZED HIS FELLOW GODS
FOR THEIR SHORTCOMINGS.

28:35.714 --> 28:39.428
AND HOW WAS HE REWARDED
FOR HIS HONESTY?

28:39.428 --> 28:41.720
THEY BANISHED HIM
FROM OLYMPUS.

28:43.142 --> 28:46.105
SO, THAT'S WHY YOU'RE HERE --
TO THREATEN ME?

28:46.105 --> 28:47.897
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:47.897 --> 28:50.519
NO, NO.
I'M HERE TO WARN YOU, SON.

28:52.521 --> 28:56.235
LOOK, SIDING WITH THAT GIRL,
WRONGED AS SHE MAY BE,

28:56.235 --> 28:58.357
SENDS A MESSAGE
TO YOUR PEERS.

28:58.357 --> 28:59.949
THESE ARE THE SAME PEOPLE

28:59.949 --> 29:02.782
WHO MAY ONE DAY
HOLD YOUR FUTURE IN THEIR HANDS.

29:02.782 --> 29:04.203
NOW,
YOU DO THIS TODAY,

29:04.203 --> 29:06.495
AND THEY WILL TURN
THEIR BACKS ON YOU

29:06.495 --> 29:09.128
JUST AS SURELY
AS THE GODS BANISHED MOMUS.

29:09.128 --> 29:11.080
YEAH, WELL, I GUESS
I'LL HAVE TO MAKE IT ON MY OWN.

29:11.080 --> 29:13.873
DANIEL, DANIEL.
[ SIGHS ]

29:13.873 --> 29:17.046
I BEG YOU
TO CONSIDER WHAT THAT MEANS.

29:17.046 --> 29:18.757
I MEAN,
DO YOU REALLY BELIEVE

29:18.757 --> 29:21.640
THAT YOU CAN STILL SUCCEED
OUT HERE IN THE REAL WORLD

29:21.640 --> 29:26.225
BASED SOLELY ON YOUR OWN,
UH, INGENUITY AND -- AND TALENT?

29:26.225 --> 29:28.347
BECAUSE I COULDN'T!

29:28.347 --> 29:30.850
AND THAT'S NOT EASY
FOR ME TO ADMIT,

29:30.850 --> 29:33.692
BUT THAT --
THAT'S THE TRUTH.

29:33.692 --> 29:38.197
LUCKILY, WE WERE BOTH BORN
WITH A GREAT ADVANTAGE --

29:38.197 --> 29:40.109
OUR FAMILY LEGACY.

29:40.109 --> 29:42.111
I MEAN,
DO YOU REALLY WANT

29:42.111 --> 29:45.034
TO THROW THAT PRECIOUS GIFT
AWAY ON THIS?

29:45.034 --> 29:48.407
ASK YOURSELF,
IS THIS THE CAUSE

29:48.407 --> 29:50.709
YOU WANT
TO RISK EVERYTHING ON?

30:05.054 --> 30:07.596
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

30:19.068 --> 30:21.780
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

30:26.325 --> 30:29.288
I DIDN'T EXPECT
TO HEAR FROM YOU.

30:29.288 --> 30:31.660
I'M AT YOUR HOTEL.
WHERE ARE YOU?

30:31.660 --> 30:33.212
[ SIGHS ]

30:33.212 --> 30:35.084
I DROVE
TO MY OLD HOUSE.

30:35.084 --> 30:36.585
DANIEL,
ARE YOU OKAY?

30:36.585 --> 30:38.417
NO.

30:38.417 --> 30:40.219
NO.

30:40.219 --> 30:41.720
I HAVEN'T BEEN
FOR AWHILE.

30:43.672 --> 30:44.924
YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT ME.

30:44.924 --> 30:45.925
No.

30:45.925 --> 30:48.177
NO, I WASN'T.

30:48.177 --> 30:51.140
THAT'S WHAT
I WANT TO TELL YOU.

30:51.140 --> 30:54.103
I WAS THE ONE RUNNING,
NOT YOU.

30:54.103 --> 30:56.315
I was doing
what my father did...

30:56.315 --> 30:59.028
DISAPPEARING
WHEN LIFE GOT HARD.

31:00.779 --> 31:02.481
BUT I DON'T WANT
TO BE LIKE HIM.

31:02.481 --> 31:04.613
I DON'T WANT
TO BE LIKE MINE.

31:04.613 --> 31:07.246
WE CAN BE BETTER TOGETHER.

31:07.246 --> 31:09.949
PLEASE, DANIEL,
COME HOME.

31:09.949 --> 31:12.121
I need you.

31:12.121 --> 31:14.043
WE NEED YOU.

31:18.207 --> 31:21.210
[ FIRE CRACKLING ]

31:24.423 --> 31:26.595
YOU WERE, UH,
UPSET WITH ME THIS MORNING

31:26.595 --> 31:31.971
FOR KEEPING SECRETS FROM YOU,
AND YOU WERE RIGHT TO BE.

31:31.971 --> 31:35.184
I DON'T WANT
TO HIDE ANYMORE.

31:35.184 --> 31:37.686
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
TELL ME ANYTHING, DAVID.
 YES, I DO.

31:37.686 --> 31:41.570
SEE, I NEVER IMAGINED THAT LIFE
COULD BE WORSE THAN PRISON.

31:41.570 --> 31:46.946
BUT NOW I HAVE HOPE, AND I KNOW
I CAN FINALLY BE FREE.

31:53.082 --> 31:55.494
TO OUR FUTURE.

31:55.494 --> 31:58.207
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

32:04.213 --> 32:06.595
[ BREATHES SHAKILY ]

32:08.177 --> 32:10.389
I-I CAN'T
KEEP DOING THIS.

32:11.640 --> 32:13.852
I CAN'T KEEP RUNNING
FROM THE TRUTH.

32:13.852 --> 32:16.015
THERE'S SOMETHING
YOU NEED TO KNOW.

32:16.015 --> 32:19.979
20 YEARS AGO,
I STOLE YOUR COMPUTER,

32:19.979 --> 32:24.523
AND I GAVE IT TO CONRAD
SO HE COULD FRAME YOU.

32:26.775 --> 32:28.617
I BETRAYED YOU.

32:30.069 --> 32:32.161
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

32:37.206 --> 32:39.418
QUITE THE COMPOUND.

32:39.418 --> 32:42.081
THOUGH IT DOESN'T SEEM
MUCH LIKE YOU.

32:42.081 --> 32:45.174
IT ISN'T.
BUT IT'S A GOOD COVER.

32:45.174 --> 32:46.295
MM.

32:46.295 --> 32:49.798
GUESS THAT WOULD EXPLAIN
THE LACK OF STAFF.

32:49.798 --> 32:51.090
[ BOTH GRUNT ]

32:51.090 --> 32:52.431
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:52.431 --> 32:55.054
MM.

32:55.054 --> 32:57.646
THIS ISN'T
GOVERNMENT ISSUE.

32:57.646 --> 32:58.977
IT'S BLACK MARKET.

32:58.977 --> 33:01.060
UNLESS
I'M SORELY MISTAKEN,

33:01.060 --> 33:03.062
WE'RE NOT DOING THIS ONE
BY THE BOOK.

33:03.062 --> 33:05.524
I DIDN'T WANT ANYTHING
TRACED BACK TO ME.

33:05.524 --> 33:07.986
[ CHUCKLES ]
IF YOU CAN'T TRUST ME, FINE.

33:07.986 --> 33:09.868
I'LL TAKE MY CHANCES
ON MY OWN.

33:09.868 --> 33:11.450
BUT THE BEST SHOT WE HAVE
OF SAVING OUR PARENTS

33:11.450 --> 33:14.323
IS TO WORK TOGETHER,
HUH?

33:21.460 --> 33:23.672
WHY ARE YOU
TELLING ME THIS NOW?

33:23.672 --> 33:26.004
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.
I ALWAYS HAVE.

33:26.004 --> 33:30.049
YOU RUINED MY LIFE
FOR MONEY.

33:30.049 --> 33:31.510
NO.

33:33.552 --> 33:35.264
I WAS AFRAID.

33:35.264 --> 33:37.056
WHAT?

33:37.056 --> 33:38.897
WHY DID YOU CHOOSE THE MAN
THAT YOU WERE AFRAID OF?

33:38.897 --> 33:40.979
I DIDN'T.
I WAS FRIGHTENED OF YOU.

33:42.441 --> 33:46.105
WE WERE GOING TO TAKE THE
CHILDREN AND START A NEW LIFE.

33:46.105 --> 33:48.857
AND I KNEW THE RISKS,
BUT I BELIEVED IN US.

33:50.649 --> 33:52.071
AND THAT'S
WHEN I FOUND OUT

33:52.071 --> 33:54.113
THE SECRET YOU'D BEEN HIDING
ABOUT YOUR WIFE.

33:54.113 --> 33:55.954
KARA?

33:55.954 --> 33:57.286
YOU TOLD ME
SHE WAS DEAD, DAVID.

33:57.286 --> 33:58.537
I BOUGHT
EVERY WORD OF IT,

33:58.537 --> 34:00.419
AND YOU MADE YOUR DAUGHTER
BELIEVE IT, TOO.

34:00.419 --> 34:02.541
SHE WAS SICK.
AMANDA WAS ONLY A CHILD.

34:02.541 --> 34:04.213
SHE WOULDN'T HAVE
UNDERSTOOD.

34:04.213 --> 34:05.834
I WOULD HAVE!

34:05.834 --> 34:10.969
I WAITED FOR YOU TO TELL ME
THE TRUTH, BUT YOU NEVER DID.

34:10.969 --> 34:14.132
AND IN THE MOMENT
I NEEDED TO TRUST YOU THE MOST,

34:14.132 --> 34:17.266
YOU MADE ME DOUBT YOU.

34:17.266 --> 34:19.768
AND I HATED YOU
FOR IT.

34:27.856 --> 34:32.690
[ Crying ] THEN CONRAD...
TOLD ME ABOUT THE BOMBING,

34:32.690 --> 34:35.072
AND DANIEL AND I
WERE TRAPPED.

34:35.072 --> 34:37.196
AND I WAS TERRIFIED
OF LOSING MY SON.

34:37.196 --> 34:43.161
AND IN MY RAGE,
I USED YOU TO GET US OUT OF IT.

34:43.161 --> 34:47.045
I SWEAR I REGRETTED
THAT DECISION EVER SINCE.

34:47.045 --> 34:49.588
DAVID, I AM SO SORRY.

34:49.588 --> 34:52.420
I'M SO SORRY.

34:52.420 --> 34:56.054
I KNOW I DON'T DESERVE
YOUR FORGIVENESS, BUT...

34:59.978 --> 35:02.981
...I'M ASKING FOR IT.

35:06.645 --> 35:08.317
SEE, NORMALLY,
I RESEARCH ALL OF MY TARGETS,

35:08.317 --> 35:11.230
BUT...THERE'S NOTHING
ON MALCOLM.

35:11.230 --> 35:14.363
HE THINKS SECRETS
MAKE HIM UNTOUCHABLE.

35:14.363 --> 35:16.695
BUT I KNOW HOW
TO DRAW HIM OUT INTO THE OPEN.

35:16.695 --> 35:19.238
WE JUST NEED
TO USE THE RIGHT BAIT.

35:19.238 --> 35:20.999
MONEY.

35:20.999 --> 35:23.242
SPECIFICALLY, THE FORTUNE
YOUR FATHER TOOK FROM HIM.

35:24.243 --> 35:26.004
OH,
HE NEVER TOLD YOU?

35:26.004 --> 35:27.836
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:27.836 --> 35:31.129
BEFORE DAVID ESCAPED, HE DRAINED
MOST OF MALCOLM'S ACCOUNTS

35:31.129 --> 35:34.383
AND FUNNELED THE MONEY
INTO CHARITIES ACROSS THE WORLD.

35:34.383 --> 35:38.927
IT WAS HIS WAY OF MAKING AMENDS
FOR THE THINGS HE'D DONE.

35:38.927 --> 35:40.719
THE THING IS,

35:40.719 --> 35:44.062
MALCOLM NEVER BELIEVED
DAVID GAVE THE MONEY AWAY.

35:44.062 --> 35:46.815
SO HE SENT YOU HERE
TO FIND IT.

35:46.815 --> 35:50.028
LUCKY FOR US, YOU HAVE ENOUGH
TO MAKE HIM THINK I DID.

35:50.028 --> 35:53.532
IF YOU WIRE THE CASH INTO
AN ACCOUNT ONLY HE CAN ACCESS --

35:53.532 --> 35:56.034
AND WE TAKE HIM DOWN
ONCE HE GOES TO CLAIM IT.

35:57.656 --> 35:58.867
THAT'S A GOOD PLAN.

35:58.867 --> 36:01.950
I GUESS
MY ONLY QUESTION IS...

36:03.782 --> 36:05.994
...WHEN WERE YOU PLANNING
ON KILLING ME?

36:08.166 --> 36:12.711
WELL, I WAS PLANNING ON
AFTER WE GOT YOUR MONEY, BUT...

36:12.711 --> 36:14.293
PLANS CHANGE.

36:14.293 --> 36:16.795
[ SIGHS ]

36:22.140 --> 36:24.683
SO, THE MOTHER STORY
WAS A LIE.

36:24.683 --> 36:26.184
BARELY.

36:26.184 --> 36:29.187
SHE IS WITH MALCOLM, BUT THAT'S
BECAUSE HE'S MY FATHER.

36:29.187 --> 36:32.861
SECRET DAUGHTER
IN THE FBI.

36:32.861 --> 36:35.234
THAT'S AN EXCELLENT
INSURANCE POLICY.

36:35.234 --> 36:37.816
GOD,
I HAVE TO KNOW.

36:37.816 --> 36:39.318
WHAT TIPPED YOU OFF?

36:39.318 --> 36:41.119
OH.

36:41.119 --> 36:43.121
I NEVER BELIEVED YOU.

36:43.121 --> 36:45.994
I JUST WANTED TO GET YOU
AWAY FROM INNOCENT CIVILIANS

36:45.994 --> 36:48.377
AND IN FRONT
OF MY SECURITY CAMERAS.

36:48.377 --> 36:50.499
OH, DON'T WORRY.
YOU WON'T SEE THEM.

36:50.499 --> 36:53.632
ONE OF THE MANY PERKS OF HAVING
A GENIUS AS A BEST FRIEND.

36:55.093 --> 36:58.547
YOUR COVER IS BLOWN.

36:58.547 --> 37:01.009
WELL, I'LL JUST HAVE TO
DELETE THE DRIVES

37:01.009 --> 37:02.100
BEFORE I GO, THEN.

37:02.100 --> 37:04.012
[ GUN CLICKS ]
 OOPS.

37:06.104 --> 37:08.016
GUESS YOU DIDN'T NOTICE
THIS TIME, EITHER.

37:08.016 --> 37:09.768
[ GRUNTS ]

37:09.768 --> 37:11.350
[ GROWLS ]

37:11.350 --> 37:13.482
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

37:13.482 --> 37:14.062
AAH!

37:22.821 --> 37:25.954
WELL, I WOULD SAY THAT A TOAST
IS IN ORDER.

37:25.954 --> 37:28.036
[ BOTTLE CAPS RATTLE ]

37:28.036 --> 37:30.248
[ CHUCKLES ]
TO EMILY AND KATE?

37:30.248 --> 37:33.332
NO, TO MY PARTY
SURVIVING UNSCATHED.

37:33.332 --> 37:36.295
I MEAN, IT'S A HAMPTONS'
FREAKIN' MIRACLE.

37:36.295 --> 37:39.508
RIGHT.
TO THE IMPORTANT STUFF.

37:43.802 --> 37:45.644
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

37:45.644 --> 37:49.017
ARE YOU STILL LOOKING
INTO KATE'S BACKGROUND?

37:49.017 --> 37:51.059
OH, YEAH.

37:51.059 --> 37:52.851
I FORGOT
THAT WAS RUNNING.

37:52.851 --> 37:55.694
UH, WHY?
ANYTHING JUICY?

37:59.568 --> 38:01.490
CALL EMILY.

38:01.490 --> 38:03.071
TELL HER NOT TO LET KATE
IN THE HOUSE!

38:03.071 --> 38:04.112
WHY?!
WHAT'S WRONG?!

38:04.112 --> 38:05.163
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

38:08.537 --> 38:10.709
OHH!

38:27.305 --> 38:28.306
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

38:43.572 --> 38:45.614
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

38:48.447 --> 38:51.450
AAH!

39:01.840 --> 39:03.672
[ GAGS, GRUNTS ]

39:07.345 --> 39:10.228
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

39:15.183 --> 39:18.026
[ BOTH GRUNT ]

39:19.237 --> 39:22.240
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

39:28.787 --> 39:31.450
AAH!

39:31.450 --> 39:33.792
AAH!

39:33.792 --> 39:37.916
[ GRUNTING ]

39:42.000 --> 39:44.002
[ GRUNTS ]

39:44.002 --> 39:45.504
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

39:52.851 --> 39:54.933
[ EMILY GRUNTING ]

39:56.224 --> 39:58.016
EMILY!

39:59.518 --> 40:00.689
WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOU?

40:00.689 --> 40:01.860
GET OUT OF HERE!
RUN!

40:01.860 --> 40:03.361
[ GRUNTING ]

40:04.733 --> 40:06.074
NO!

40:12.871 --> 40:14.202
DROP IT!

40:25.844 --> 40:28.216
WHY DIDN'T YOU LISTEN
TO ME, DANIEL?

40:28.216 --> 40:31.219
I TOLD YOU TO RUN!

40:31.219 --> 40:34.312
WHY DIDN'T YOU RUN?

40:36.014 --> 40:39.768
Daniel: "DEAR DAD,
MY WHOLE LIFE, I'VE BEEN TOLD

40:39.768 --> 40:41.439
"I WAS DESTINED FOR GREATNESS

40:41.439 --> 40:44.653
"BASED SOLELY
ON THE VIRTUE OF MY NAME.

40:44.653 --> 40:47.616
"I WAS TAUGHT
SACRIFICE WAS FOR THE FOOLISH.

40:47.616 --> 40:50.198
"SURVIVAL WAS ALL
THAT MATTERED.

40:50.198 --> 40:53.331
"BUT NOW I FIND MYSELF
AT A CROSSROADS,

40:53.331 --> 40:57.165
"AND I MUST DECIDE
WHAT I BELIEVE TO BE TRUE.

40:57.165 --> 41:00.418
"THERE IS NO SUCH THING
AS DESTINY.

41:00.418 --> 41:03.461
"LEGACIES MUST BE EARNED
BY THE CHOICES WE MAKE.

41:03.461 --> 41:07.135
"I NOW KNOW
THAT WE WRITE OUR OWN ENDINGS,

41:07.135 --> 41:11.429
"AND WE CAN EITHER CHOOSE
TO HIDE AS VILLAINS

41:11.429 --> 41:14.052
OR LIVE AS HEROES."

41:14.052 --> 41:15.974
[ SNIFFLES ]

41:15.974 --> 41:17.896
YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY,
DANIEL.

41:17.896 --> 41:19.057
YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY.

41:19.057 --> 41:21.059
YOU'RE STILL LYING
TO ME.

41:21.059 --> 41:23.481
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

41:23.481 --> 41:26.234
[ GROANS ]

41:29.868 --> 41:32.871
I WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT IT WASN'T ALL A LIE.

41:34.873 --> 41:36.114
NOT WITH YOU.

41:36.114 --> 41:38.997
I KNOW.

41:38.997 --> 41:41.880
I KNOW.

41:57.185 --> 41:59.187
[ SIGHS ]
